result.name: Prohibition Grill House and Cocktail Bar

reviews.text: Great food and the staff are friendly. Good selection of drinks. Try the cocktails before meal, is worth it.

Semi buffet set lunch. A salad bar with cheese and cold cuts for first course. A selection of mains and then dessert and fruit buffet with tea or coffee. Delicious food, fresh and a good variety. Mains were on the small side but with the semi buffet style this works well. Located a few minutes from Ocean Park MTR Station and within the Marriott hotel. No need to be hotel or park guests for access.

Beautiful bar and steak house setup in the brand new Marriott Hotel next to Ocean Park.

Modern fittings with an intimate ambience. Large floor to ceiling window opens to the outdoor pool area. The customised lightings and fittings are commendable.

Good choice of whiskies and wines with good US representation.

Food is good. Fine ingredients and well executed in general.

A bit out of the way but worth the trip. It's certainly good to see some high quality F&B establishment in the area being developed.
Good buffet selection, mains and free flow drinks until 3pm.  Desserts are not replenished so not much choice after 2pm so get in early.
Nice steakhouse in the Ocean Park Marriott. Their grand opening discount is a good bargain and available during weekday/until end of May.

result.formatted_address: 180 Wong Chuk Hang Rd, Ocean Park, Hong Kong
result.name: Hong Kong Ocean Park Marriott Hotel

reviews.text: It's the birthday of my daughter Mildred and we decided to try this new hotel restaurants. The location is convenient and took us 5 minutes walk from the Ocean park station. The menu it's no different from any hotel buffet put the quality of the food was of first notch. Waiters were very helpful and offer an instant free membership with 30% discount. Highly recommended.

The two stars are for the service. Although we have pre booked a pickup car from the airport, they forgot to send it. The room was set up for two guests and not three. No welcome, no breakfast time or location information and the room reeked of fresh wood varnish. It was so strong that we all had a headache, we could taste it!  
This is just day one 🙁 
The view is nice but.

Visited Marina Kitchen in mid-May and Canton Bistro in early June. Food was good, service was good, but there's still room   for improvement for valet parking. During my first visit, on a day which they were quite busy, the parking staff drove my car away before I got my baby off the car. And during my second visit, the staff failed to start the car (MT) engine for several times.

Breakfast is amazing, lots of variety and high quality selections, hotel staff is friendly and proper and the rooms are clean and modern. Amazing location if you plan to visit ocean park as the two are connected, however some facilities may be closed due to maintenance at times so I would double check before booking if you're veering towards a specific attraction
One photo in-deeded but it shows the quality of the banquet and services is excellent. A recommended place for banquet or conference 🧸

result.formatted_address: 香港海洋公園黃竹坑道180號
result.name: 香港海洋公園萬豪酒店

reviews.text: It's the birthday of my daughter Mildred and we decided to try this new hotel restaurants. The location is convenient and took us 5 minutes walk from the Ocean park station. The menu it's no different from any hotel buffet put the quality of the food was of first notch. Waiters were very helpful and offer an instant free membership with 30% discount. Highly recommended.

地點非常方便，地鐵一出來走3分鐘就達飯店大堂，也可以直接入園，由3棟建物圍成，中間是戶外戲水池（泳池7-21），健身房24小時，房間冷氣可以很冷，衛浴採德國duravit,hansgrohe，不過以萬豪這種星級飯店插座竟沒有提供萬用插座，手機可以用USB充電，但是筆電無解，早餐提供樣式豐富但是口味不怎樣
另外善用禮賓部服務，加分不少

最後給飯店管理層建議，旺季人多，check-in，行李櫃台都忙的不可開交，但是飯店設計指標不清，入門多，對於初次入住者只能尋找服務人員的幫助，然後動線不良，死角多，還有員工找地方偷懶滑手機（不敬業）
Check in check out順暢， 離開時胃痛職員送了一枝水協助食藥。 房間裝修木調及海洋氣息為主，浴室有情調，用thann 沐浴品非常舒適，整體餐飲不錯，早餐自助餐款式都多選擇，熱香餅和窩夫由其出色！  早餐地點開揚舒服！  如早餐service (etc收碟)  好一點就perfect !
座落地鐵站旁邊，行一分鐘便到達海洋公園，環境舒適又清潔，員工服務態度很好，自助餐有很多海鮮菜色，帶子刺身非常正，還有香港特色小食—雞蛋仔。
宴會廳寬敞，40多席食品上菜快，味道可口，酒店地點交通方便，貼鄰地鐵站出口，婚宴排對好選擇
